{"tid":2049362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄外交部：G7擴大會議沒有中國參加很難解決全球 性問題","createTime":"2020-06-03T11:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T11:57:42.000Z","uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9cab4f1575ee80dede28897fb7ee24a5a76abfac","tid":2049362,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"當地時間6月2日，針對美國總統特朗普提議邀請俄羅斯參加今年的G7擴大會議，俄羅斯外交部發言人扎哈羅娃表示，沒有中國參加的G7擴大會議，很難解決全球性問題。扎哈羅娃說：&ldquo;擴大G7會議參與國這一路線是正確的，但是很明顯，沒有中國的參與，將很難解決具有全球性意義的問題。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n扎哈羅娃同時還表示，美國總統特朗普認為G7是非常過時的國家集團，並不符合當今世界的發展形勢，俄羅斯對這一觀點表示同意。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯認為在西方國家的&ldquo;排外俱樂部&rdquo;框架下無法解決目前的國際政治和經濟問題，這是客觀現實。扎哈羅娃還特別提到了二十國集團(G20)，她認為這是一個非常有效的對話模式，其中既包含G7成員國，也包含金磚國家。"},{"pid":"bcef0236fedde880fbc806a182da6e4fb204d9fc","tid":2049362,"uid":166405,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"解決左中國咪無問題"},{"pid":"9d33ed725c0aa52cc8186490127174a8c33699f7","tid":2049362,"uid":250082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"因為中國就係嗰個全球性問題"},{"pid":"3d16784d624c0babd4c92120c3c7846ec0962853","tid":2049362,"uid":167326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"中共有撚幫過忙咩～ 咪又係賴屎賴屁話自己冇問題唔肯改 同啲死廢老一樣。"},{"pid":"516e68eed5d46a366f50a0f5c6f04c01c747eb1a","tid":2049362,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcef0236fedde880fbc806a182da6e4fb204d9fc","tid":2049362,"uid":166405,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"解決左中國咪無問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:52:58.000Z","msg":"無咗中國嘅話俄羅斯就會少咗一票"},{"pid":"ccd725f4d1ea148354961a97bcb1ab97972ba2c9","tid":2049362,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"你係咪想要中國代表？<br />\n好，叫埋蔡英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92cf3a3ee32c30525e25166ff65dbdeebef8749","tid":2049362,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"因為要討論點解決中國"},{"pid":"79c3b1bc3999dc69cfb91f80e5d0c0fb8293ba44","tid":2049362,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ccd725f4d1ea148354961a97bcb1ab97972ba2c9","tid":2049362,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"你係咪想要中國代表？<br />\n好，叫埋蔡英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}